{"tid":211491,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"男生見工髮型 邊款髮型最冧HR？","createTime":"2017-04-21T16:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T01:18:29.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28f10f6acaa8335fb9bc1ecbc939c719bf8c8d0b","tid":211491,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1780000/1782945/hair_inline_20170420_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1780000%2F1782945%2Fhair_inline_20170420_c_1024.jpg&h=8f769135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然俗語有云Your face，Your fate，但其實起碼職場上面，除了face，hair都好緊要！<br />\n<br />\n大學生即將畢業，是時候搵工了，如果想見工前先整個靚髮型，不妨參考這個調查。日本資生堂連同就職網站Mynavi進行調查，詢問645位日本企業的面試官對求職者髮型的意見。其中，8成面試官認同，求職者髮型會影響對他的第一印象，而且大部分人（95.5%）都同意，與求職者初見面時的第一印象很影響最終的評分。<br />\n<br />\n清爽短髮最佳　長髮染金差評<br />\n<br />\n調查準備了20種男生髮型的相片讓面試官評分，其中最遭劣評的是偏長、厚身的卷髮與染成明亮色系的髮型。<br />\n<br />\n如果求職者髮型長至見不到額頭，面試官普遍會覺得他欠缺自信、甚至覺得他性格很陰沉。<br />\n<br />\n如果染成閃亮金色，又覺得不夠認真，不似在求職。相對，最受好評的是各種短髮，大原則是讓五官表情清晰可見，清爽示人，展現活力又不失成熟。<br />\n<br />\n至於女生髮型變化就更加多，CT Goodjobs早前曾推介幾款女生見工合適髮型，可供參考：<br />\n<br />\n1. 斯文公主頭：<br />\n<br />\n中長髮搵工女面試時，最適合梳個讓面容看起來清新乾淨的公主頭，能給面試官自然、亮麗的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n2. 清爽馬尾Look：<br />\n<br />\n馬尾頭的造型感覺比較利落；為加強親切感，綁馬尾時瀏海最好凸出弧度。馬尾紮髮的位置須恰到到好處&mdash;&mdash;即唔太高亦唔太低；綁太高容易顯得過分活潑；太低則會顯得「C9」。<br />\n<br />\n3. 優雅髮髻：<br />\n<br />\n髮髻最能展現事業女優雅的一面，更有助提升專業形象。嫌傳統髮髻過於成熟的話，求職者不妨加個低調頭飾，凸顯心思，務求令面試官眼前一亮。<br />\n<br />\n4. 波浪微曲髮：<br />\n<br />\n捲曲度較大的髮型，能讓頭髮看起來更豐盈、臉形更飽滿自信，使求職者看起來更可靠、溫柔，別具氣質。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1782945/?r=mcsdfb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1782945%2F%3Fr%3Dmcsdfb2&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=667a969c\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1782945/?r=mcsdfb2</a>"},{"pid":"d94f9f94aa35a69f678024f43ff657bf8c17319c","tid":211491,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"riiiiiiicko頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c478a8fa9c7c3e1709ec8d431d654b6ff34dba84","tid":211491,"uid":52418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:14:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"858729cd34d5f588642d39236f8db1e746a473d5","tid":211491,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解冇光頭啊！！<br />\n<br />\n光頭仔係唔係未見即死？</blockquote><br />\n髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fef7db7dd2ba29db166f9d0b8ae4abf65f0eb71","tid":211491,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T17:39:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解冇光頭啊！！<br />\n<br />\n光頭仔係唔係未見即死？</blockquote><br />\n髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341dba7275c23d3fdb8f937f29bf475d41c7be03","tid":211491,"uid":53786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T18:16:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解冇光頭啊！！<br />\n<br />\n光頭仔係唔係未見即死？</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">髮</span>型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9017c642128df271484dc9d101f7bd09b8dd3c83","tid":211491,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T23:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>點解冇光頭啊！！<br />\n<br />\n光頭仔係唔係未見即死？</blockquote><br />\n髮型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"